PrecisAppointment of JO MARK ZUREL of St. John's, Newfoundland and Labrador, to be a director of the board of directors of the Canada Pension Plan Investment Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term ending October 26, 2014, in the place of Elaine McKinnon.
